  "title": "SALES ADMIN EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description &amp; Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Answering telephone calls from clients.</li>\n  <li>Replying to email enquiries with standard template.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate sales manager schedules for meeting with clients.</li>\n  <li>Utilize company resources to develop a filling system that keeps      all active sales files available digitally and in hard copy form.</li>\n  <li>Coordinating with sales manager in filling important documents and      communicating relevant information.</li>\n  <li>Data entry in cater master.</li>\n  <li>Send EDM and proposal.</li>\n  <li>Sending thank you letter/after sales support.</li>\n  <li>Send BEO distribution to relevant department.</li>\n  <li>Send introduction email accordingly to properties with standard template provided.</li>\n  <li>Send emails to clients with regards to the appointed Vendors information and details.</li>\n  <li>Sit down with Sales Managers as and when needed with their clients.</li>\n  <li>Act as the primary customer service contact for clients who have questions about their accounts or our services.</li>\n  <li>Checking prices and contracts are up to date.</li>\n  <li>Prepare weekly forecast and sales report.</li>\n  <li>To key in new leads in Cater Master system under ‘<strong>Enquiry</strong>’</li>\n  <li>Check with Sales Manager on packages to create ‘<strong>Proposal</strong>’</li>\n  <li>Create the skeleton of ‘<strong>Contract</strong>’ as and when required</li>\n  <li>Email blast to new list, and past customers to touch base</li>\n  <li>Update property ‘<strong>Event Revenue Forecast'</strong></li>\n  <li>Take down minute for any meeting attended</li>\n  <li>Submit daily report end of each working day</li>\n  <li>Meet with guests and clients</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Proven work experience as a Sales administrator or Sales support or Telemarketing</li>\n  <li>Excellent organizational and multitasking skills</li>\n  <li>A team player with high level of dedication</li>\n  <li>Ability to work under strict deadlines</li>\n  <li>Attractive incentive</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office, and use of telephone systems</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and presentation skills</li>\n  <li>Warm, welcoming and approachable voice</li>\n  <li>Training will be provided.</li>\n</ul>",
